021%2C%20when%20Bezos%20announced%20that%20he%20was%20transitioning%20to%20the%20executive%20chair%20of%20the%20Amazon%20Board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20to%20employees%20then%2C%20Bezos%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAndy%20is%20well%20known%20inside%20the%20company%20and%20has%20been%20at%20Amazon%20almost%20as%20long%20as%20I%20have.%20He%20will%20be%20an%20outstanding%20leader%2C%20and%20he%20has%20my%20full%20confidence.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENet%20worth%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-ceo-andy-jassy-total-pay-compensation-explained-2023-4%5C%22%3EJassy's%20total%20compensation%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20%24212%20million%20including%20stock%20and%20a%20base%20salary%20of%20%24175%2C000.%20His%20total%20pay%20dropped%20to%20%241.3%20million%20in%202022%2C%20including%20a%20base%20salary%20of%20%24317%2C500%2C%20according%20to%20an%20SEC%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20drop%20was%20linked%20to%20Amazon's%20declining%20stock%20price.%20Jassy%20owned%20about%202%20million%20shares%20of%20Amazon%20as%20of%20early%202023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECareer%2C%20background%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJassy%20grew%20up%20in%20Scarsdale%2C%20New%20York.%20He%20attended%20Harvard%20University%20and%20has%20an%20MBA%20from%20Harvard%20Business%20School%2C%20according%20to%20LinkedIn.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20worked%20for%20the%20collectibles%20company%20MBI%20as%20a%20project%20manager%20before%20joining%20Amazon%20as%20a%20marketing%20manager%20in%201997.%20He%20held%20several%20roles%20within%20Amazon%20in%20both%20the%20business-to-business%20and%20business-to-consumer%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202003%2C%20Jassy%20and%20Bezos%20developed%20the%20idea%20for%20AWS%2C%20which%20was%20launched%20three%20years%20later.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJassy%20serves%20on%20the%20Trust%20of%20the%20American%20Academy%20of%20Arts%20and%20Sciences%2C%20on%20the%20Board%20of%20Trustees%20for%20Rainier%20Scholars%2C%20and%20as%20Chair%20of%20Rainier%20Prep's%20Board%20of%20Directors.%20He's%20also%20a%20minority%20owner%20of%20the%20NHL%20team%20Seattle%20Kraken.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EStance%20on%20remote%20work%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon's%20employees%20and%20leadership%20team%20have%20clashed%20over%20remote%20work%20policies%20since%20Jassy%20became%20CEO.%20Managers%20are%20now%20allowed%20to%20effectively%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-lets-managers-terminate-employees-return-to-office-2023-10%5C%22%3Efire%20employees%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20fail%20to%20comply%20with%20Amazon's%20return-to-office%20mandate%20after%20months%20of%20internal%20turmoil.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20Amazon%20started%20forcing%20staff%20to%20relocate%20near%20central%20%26quot%3Bhub%26quot%3B%20offices%20or%20take%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-andy-jassy-no-data-return-to-office-rto-aws-2023-8%5C%22%3Evoluntary%20resignation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20infuriating%20some%20workers%20who%20had%20already%20been%20asked%20to%20return%20to%20the%20office%20at%20least%20three%20days%20per%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJassy%20gave%20an%20internal%20interview%20in%20August%20where%20he%20addressed%20RTO%2C%20after%20which%20an%20internal%20Slack%20channel%20about%20remote%20work%20quickly%20filled%20up%20with%20dozens%20of%20critical%20employee%20reactions%2C%20according%20to%20screenshots%20obtained%20by%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20people%20were%20disappointed%20by%20Jassy's%20failure%20to%20provide%20clear%20data%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceo-entrepreneur-remote-work-benefits-individuals-but-impacts-teams-2023-6%5C%22%3Ein-office%20work's%20benefits%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Amazon%20is%20notorious%20for%20making%20key%20data-based%20decisions%2C%20but%20some%20employees%20felt%20the%20RTO%20decision%20was%20being%20made%20arbitrarily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20data%20when%20we%20were%20deciding%20to%20pursue%20AWS%2C%20which%20was%20quite%20different%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20our%20businesses%20at%20that%20time%2C%20that%20we%20were%20going%20to%20be%20successful.%20In%20fact%2C%20most%20people%20thought%20it%20was%20nuts%20internally%20and%20externally%2C%26quot%3B%20Jassy%20said%20during%20the%20meeting%2C%20internally%20called%20a%20%26quot%3BFishbowl.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20were%20judgment%20decisions%20by%20our%20leadership%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20Jassy%20continued.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that%20is%20what's%20happened%20here.%20As%20a%20leadership%20team%2C%20we've%20decided%20that%20we%20will%20be%20better%20for%20customers%20and%20for%20our%20business%20being%20in%20the%20office.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ELeadership%20style%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20his%20promotion%20to%20CEO%2C%20he%20was%20considered%20an%20%26quot%3Bauthentic%2C%20genuine%2C%20empathetic%26quot%3B%20boss%2C%20company%20insiders%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20doesn't%20suffer%20foolishness%2C%26quot%3B%20Scott%20Chancellor%2C%20a%20former%20AWS%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECurrent%20and%20former%20AWS%20employees%20also%20told%20Insider%20that%20Jassy%20has%20operated%20with%20almost%20complete%20autonomy%20at%20Amazon%20prior%20to%20becoming%20CEO.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJeff%20has%20allowed%20Andy%20to%20do%20his%20job%20without%20anybody%20looking%20over%20his%20shoulder%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20former%20senior-level%20employee%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20100%25%20Andy's%20show.%20Jeff%20does%20not%20tell%20Andy%20what%20to%20do.%20...%20They're%20almost%20side-by-side%20on%20the%20org%20chart.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAvery%20Hartmans%20contributed%20to%20an%20earlier%20version%20of%20this%20report.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandy-jassy%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Inside