nna-convention%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20United%20States%20and%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20also%20issued%20statements%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20Friday%20claiming%20that%20the%20insistence%20on%20the%2041%20diplomats%E2%80%99%20withdrawal%20was%20not%20in%20line%20with%20obligations%20under%20the%20Vienna%20convention.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20had%20not%20officially%20responded%20to%20the%20UK%20and%20US%E2%80%99%20statements%2C%20but%20Jaishankar%20said%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbig%20concern%E2%80%9D%20was%20the%20suspension%20of%20visa%20services%20by%20the%20Indian%20high%20commission%20and%20two%20consulates%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSome%20weeks%20ago%2C%20we%20stopped%20issuing%20visas%20in%20Canada%20because%20it%20was%20no%20longer%20safe%20for%20our%20diplomats%20to%20go%20to%20work%20to%20issue%20visas.%20So%20their%20safety%20and%20security%20was%20the%20primary%20reason%20we%20had%20to%20temporarily%20stop%20the%20issue%20of%20visas%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20on%20Sunday%20at%20an%20interaction.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20had%20stopped%20visa%20operations%20after%20Canadian%20prime%20minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20had%20accused%20Indian%20government%20agents%20of%20being%20involved%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20a%20Canadian%20national%20who%20is%20described%20as%20a%20terrorist%20by%20authorities%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fwatch-has-jaishankar-been-able-to-influence-the-us-response-to-the-india-canada-crisis%5C%22%3EHas%20Jaishankar%20Been%20Able%20to%20Influence%20the%20US%20Response%20to%20the%20India-Canada%20Crisis%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20Indian%20move%20was%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20expulsion%20of%20a%20Canadian%20diplomat%20in%20a%20tit-for-tat%20measure.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20India%20had%20also%20sought%20%E2%80%9Cparity%E2%80%9D%20in%20diplomatic%20representation%20in%20both%20countries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fmedia-briefings.htm%3Fdtl%2F37134%2FTranscript_of_Weekly_Media_Briefing_by_the_Official_Spokesperson_September_21_2023%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20September%2021%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20external%20affairs%20ministry%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20said%20that%20India%20will%20%E2%80%9Ccontinue%20to%20review%20this%20situation%20on%20a%20regular%20basis%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20the%20assessment%20on%20the%20security%20environment%20for%20Indian%20diplomats%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20be%20going%20on%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20Jaishankar%20for%20the%20first%20time%20publicly%20indicated%20that%20a%20review%20was%20underway.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99re%20tracking%20it%20very%20closely.%20My%20hope%2C%20my%20expectation%2C%20is%20that%20%5Bthe%5D%20situation%20would%20improve%20in%20the%20sense%20that%20our%20people%20would%20have%20greater%20confidence%20in%20being%20able%20to%20do%20their%20basic%20duty%20as%20diplomats%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jaishankar%20said.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CBecause%20ensuring%20%5Bthe%5D%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20diplomats%20is%20the%20most%20fundamental%20aspect%20of%20the%20Vienna%20Convention.%20And%20right%20now%2C%20that%20is%20what%20has%20in%20many%20ways%20been%20challenged%20in%20Canada%2C%20that%20our%20people%20are%20not%20safe%2C%20our%20diplomats%20are%20not%20safe.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20if%20we%20see%20progress%20there%2C%20I%20would%20like%20very%20much%20to%20resume%20the%20issue%20of%20visas.%20My%20hope%20would%20be%20that%20it%20would%20be%20something%20which%20should%20happen%20very%20soon%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndian%20official%20sources%20further%20reinforced%20the%20minister%E2%80%99s%20messaging%20that%20indicated%20that%20an%20imminent%20decision%20was%20in%20the%20wings%20by%20highlighting%20Jaishankar%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20that%20India%20was%20%E2%80%9Creviewing%20the%20security%20situation%20that%20led%20to%20the%20suspension%20of%20visa%20services%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Findia-canada-fake-news-punjabis-visa%5C%22%3EWorried%20Over%20India-Canada%20Situation%2C%20Punjabis%20in%20Both%20Countries%20Decry%20Fake%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJaishankar%20also%20defended%20India%E2%80%99s%20insistence%20on%20parity%20with%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20diplomatic%20strength.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20invoked%20parity%20because%20we%20had%20concerns%20about%20continuous%20interference%20in%20our%20affairs%20by%20Canadian%20personnel.%20We%20haven%E2%80%99t%20made%20much%20of%20that%20public.%20My%20sense%20is%20that%20over%20a%20period%20of%20time%2C%20more%20stuff%20will%20come%20out%20and%20people%20will%20understand%20why%20we%20had%20the%20kind%20of%20discomfort%20with%20many%20of%20them%20which%20we%20did%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20substantial%20section%20of%20the%20Canadian%20population%20is%20of%20Indian%20origin%20and%20has%20been%20deeply%20worried%20about%20the%20resumption%20of%20Indian%20visa%20operations%2C%20with%20most%20of%20them%20not%20having%20overseas%20citizen%20of%20India%20cards.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Canadian%20decision%20to%20suspend%20%E2%80%98walk-in%E2%80%99%20services%20at%20consulates%20and%20the%20drastic%20cutting%20down%20of%20immigration%20officials%20in%20India%20meant%20that%20there%20would%20be%20a%20large%20backlog%20in%20processing%20applications.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20Canadian%20media%20reports%2C%2045%25%20of%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20inte