e%20applications%20submitted%2C%20he%20still%20panicked%3A%20%26quot%3BShouldn't%20I%20apply%20to%20other%20schools%3F%20There%20have%20to%20be%20more!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20again%20went%20through%20the%20list%20of%20campuses%20he%20toured.%20He%20thought%20about%20the%20college%20reps%20who'd%20visited%20his%20high%20school.%20He%20didn't%20feel%20as%20if%20any%20other%20options%20were%20as%20appealing%20as%20his%20original%20three.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20just%20accept%20that%20this%20is%20your%20list%20and%20be%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20advised%2C%20seeing%20no%20need%20for%20him%20to%20waste%20his%20time%20or%20our%20money%20by%20applying%20to%20places%20in%20which%20he%20had%20no%20interest%20just%20to%20hit%20some%20arbitrary%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20he%20agreed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEveryone%20was%20shocked%20that%20he%20was%20applying%20to%20only%203%20schools%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Ben%2C%20his%20dad%2C%20and%20I%20were%20comfortable%20with%20this%20decision%2C%20others%20seemed%20shocked%20and%20concerned.%20When%20people%20asked%20where%20he'd%20applied%20and%20we%20listed%20the%20schools%2C%20they'd%20stammer%3A%20%26quot%3BThat's%20it%3F!%20Why%3F%20What%20will%20you%20do%20if%20he%20doesn't%20get%20into%20one%20of%20those%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20assured%20them%20we'd%20cross%20that%20bridge%20if%20we%20had%20to%20after%20the%20decisions%20arrived.%20That%20seemed%20to%20stress%20them%20out%20even%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20Ben%20got%20into%20his%20safety%20as%20well%20as%20his%20top%20choice.%20It%20was%20a%20relief%20to%20have%20the%20decision%20made%2C%20and%20we%20were%20glad%20he'd%20resisted%20the%20urge%20to%20flood%20admission%20portals%20just%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EUltimately%2C%20we%20did%20what%20was%20right%20for%20Ben%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20college-application%20process%20has%20become%20notoriously%20nerve