20disastrous%2C%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-bloody-human-wave-tactics-ukraine-white-house-says-2023-10%5C%22%3Epersonnel%2C%20weapons%2C%20and%20armor%20losses%20piling%20up%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Ukraine%20continues%20to%20target%20occupied%20Crimea%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20making%20it%20untenable.%20Black%20Sea%20forces%20have%20been%20pummeled%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussias-weak-defenses-letting-ukrainian-drone-boats-blow-holes-warships-2023-8%5C%22%3Echeap%20drone%20boats%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20list%20goes%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20possibility%20is%20that%20Putin's%20readying%20the%20Burevestnik%20as%20a%20bargaining%20chip%20%E2%80%94%20he%20likes%20to%20rattle%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fex-cia-officer-putin-cornered-nuclear-weapons-ukraine-chances-increasing-2022-9%5C%22%3Enuclear%20saber%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20what%20he%20wants.%C2%A0The%20Burevestnik%20gives%20him%2C%20Podvig%20said%2C%20a%20chance%20to%20say%20that%20Russia%20has%20a%20unique%20weapon%20in%20its%20arsenal.%20That%20may%20be%20enough%20at%20the%20negotiating%20table.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fputin-nuclear-powered-cruise-missile-unnecessary-not-totally-useless-expert-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697984101000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F617319934f9d8b0011afbedc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fputin-nuclear-powered-cruise-missile-unnecessary-not-totally-useless-expert-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Even%20if%20Putin's%20claim%20of%20a%20successful%20test%20of%20the%20Burevestnik%20is%20true%2C%20it%20doesn't%20really%20change%20much.%20It's%20more%20for%20show%2C%20an%20expert%20told%20Insider.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cpanella%40insider.com%