%20base%20in%20southern%20Israel%20on%20October%2015%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EAlon%20Bernstein%2FAP%20Photo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EHamas%20militants%20who%20carried%20out%20the%20October%207%20attacks%20on%20Israel%20may%20have%20used%20North%20Korean%20weapons.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EIsrael%20captured%20a%20number%20of%20North%20Korean%20F-7%20rocket-propelled%20grenades%20during%20the%20fighting.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ENorth%20Korea%20denied%20the%20claims%2C%20but%20it%20has%20long%20been%20linked%20with%20supporting%20Palestinian%20militant%20groups%2C%20experts%20say.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EHamas%20militants%20likely%20used%20some%20weapons%20from%20North%20Korea%20in%20the%20October%207%20terrorist%20attacks%20on%20Israel%2C%20arms%20experts%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20forces%20seized%20a%20number%20of%20North%20Korean%20F-7%20rocket-propelled%20grenades%20(RPG)%20from%20the%20Palestinian%20militant%20group%20during%20the%20conflict%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhosted.ap.org%2Farticle%2F703e33663ea299f920d0d14039adfbb8%2Fevidence-shows-hamas-militants-likely-used-some-north%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Associated%20Press%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESouth%20Korea's%20Joint%20Chiefs%20of%20Staff%20also%20told%20journalists%20that%20it%20believed%20Hamas%20used%20the%20F-7%20in%20the%20attack%2C%20per%20The%20AP%2C%20while%20The%20Washington%20Post%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2F10%2F21%2Fhamas-documents-plans-israel-attack%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eobtained%20a%20Hamas%20field%20manual%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20dated%20to%20last%20year%2C%20that%20was%20found%20on%20the%20body%20of%20one%20fighter%20and%20that%20included%20instructions%20on%20how%20to%20operate%20F-7%20RPGs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNorth%20Korea%20has%20long%20supported%20Palestinian%20militant%20groups%2C%