2left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104629468.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EActress%20Gauahar%20Khan%20recently%20shared%20an%20incident%20from%20when%20she%20was%2018%2C%20where%20she%20encountered%20a%20famous%20person%20who%20made%20her%20feel%20uncomfortable%20during%20an%20interview.%20The%20individual%20held%20her%20hand%20throughout%20the%20conversation%2C%20leaving%20her%20feeling%20awkward%20and%20unsure%20of%20how%20to%20react.%20After%20the%20shoot%2C%20the%20person%20even%20tried%20to%20ask%20for%20her%20number.%20Gauahar%20followed%20her%20director's%20advice%20to%20stay%20locked%20in%20her%20room%2C%20later%20learning%20that%20the%20star%20was%20upset%20she%20didn't%20meet%20him%20before%20leaving.%20Gauahar%20Khan%20and%20her%20husband%20Zaid%20Darbar%20recently%20welcomed%20their%20baby%20boy%20named%20Zehaan.%20She%20will%20also%20be%20hosting%20%26quot%3BJhalak%20Dikhhla%20Jaa%2011%26quot%3B%20with%20Rithvik%20Dhanjani.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fgauahar-khan-reveals-that-a-big-star-made-her-uncomfortable-he-wouldnt-let-go-of-my-hand%2Farticleshow%2F104629468.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Modi%20Government%20Move%20to%20Turn%20Government%20Officers%20into%20%E2%80%98Rath%20Prabharis%E2%80%99%20Stirs%20Storm%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F22171955%2FF8OlZAaXEAAeXHw.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9CThe%20struggle%20of%20man%20against%20power%20is%20the%20struggle%20of%20memory%20against%20forgetting%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20celebrated%20Czech-French%20novelist%20Milan%20Kundera.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20merit%20of%20a%20circular%20issued%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20on%20October%2017%20to%20all%20the%20ministries%2C%20which%20has%20since%20been%20circulating%20widely%20on%20social%20media%20for%20its%20shock%20value%2C%20fits%20perfectly%20around%20Kundera%E2%80%99s%20words.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20circular%20has%20a%20categorical%20ask%3A%20Nominate%20officers%20of%20the%20rank%20of%20joint%20secretaries%2Fdirector%2Fdeputy%20secretary%20till%20the%20gram%20panchayat%20level%20in%20all%20the%20765%20districts%20of%20the%20country%20to%20deploy%20them%20as%20%E2%80%9Cdistrict%20rath%20prabharis%20(special%20officers)%E2%80%9D%20between%20November%2020%2C%202023%20and%20January%2025%2C%202024%20to%20%E2%80%9Cshowcase%2Fcelebrate%20the%20achievements%20of%20the%20last%20nine%20years%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2021%2C%20former%20secretary%20in%20the%20Union%20government%20E.A.S.%20Sarma%20wrote%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20to%20intervene%20at%20once%20and%20revoke%20the%20order.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20the%20best%20of%20my%20knowledge%2C%20the%20above%20instructions%20were%20issued%20when%20the%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20had%20already%20come%20into%20force%20and%2C%20as%20such%2C%20they%20amount%20to%20its%20brazen%20infringement%2C%20as%20they%20place%20the%20NDA%20government%20at%20an%20advantage%20vis-%C3%A0-vis%20the%20political%20parties%20in%20opposition%2C%20amounting%20to%20misuse%20of%20government%20machinery%20for%20activity%20that%20will%20influence%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20all%20ministries%2C%20including%20the%20defence%20ministry%2C%20have%20issued%20orders%20to%20nominate%20officials%20to%20be%20%E2%80%98Rath%20Prabharis%E2%80%99%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20promote%20its%20government%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20polls%2C%20the%20senior%20bureaucrat%20also%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20serious%20concern%20that%20officers%20of%20the%20Defence%20Forces%20should%20be%20mis-deployed%20for%20showcasing%20the%20NDS%20government%E2%80%99s%20achievements.%20It%20may%20not%20be%20appropriate%20in%20the%20long%20run.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBy%20mid-day%2C%20former%20IAS%20officer%20M.G.%20Devasahayam%20also%20wrote%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20endorsing%20Sarma%E2%80%99s%20letter.%20The%20Election%20Commission%20is%20yet%20to%20react%20to%20these%20letters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFormer%20cabinet%20secretary%20B.K.%20Chaturvedi%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20unprecedented.%20I%20have%20not%20seen%20any%20such%20thing%20in%20my%20entire%20civil%20service%20career.%20It%20will%20be%20seen%20as%20politicisation%20of%20civil%20and%20defence%20services.%20The%20government%20has%20publicity%20departments%20whose%20job%20it%20is%20to%20publicise%20its%20work.%20Using%20senior%20civil%20servants%20and%20defence%20personnel%20in%20special%20campaigns%20is%20improper%20in%20the%20context%20of%20impending%20elections%20in%20the%20states%20to%20be%20followed%20by%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFormer%20member%20of%20the%20Planning%20Commission%20N.C.%20Saxena%20also%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%5BI%E2%80%99ve%5D%20never%20seen%20such%20a%20publicity%20programme%20involving%20civil%20servants.%20It%20is%20blurring%20the%20line%20between%20civil%20service%20and%20politics.%20On%20the%20one%20hand%20all%20data%20systems%20which%20assess%20performance%2C%20like%20NSSO%20and%20NFHS%2C%20are%20being%20undermined%20as%20seen%20in%20the%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fks-james-iips-director-resignation-nfhs-health-ministry%5C%22%3Eresignation%20of%20the%20head%20of%20NFHS%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20the%20other%20such%20programmes%20are%20being%20created%20to%20publicise%20government%20performance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20October%2017%20circular%2C%20Congress%20spokespersons%20like%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20and%20Pawan%20Khera%20took%20to%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20on%20October%2021%20to%20question%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20action.%20A%20day%20later%2C%20party%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20wrote%20to%20the%20prime%20minister%20%E2%80%9Con%20the%20blatant%20politicisation%20taking%20place%20of%20civil%20servants%20and%20soldiers%20who%20must%20at%20all%20times%20be%20kept%20independent%20and%20non-political%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20clear%20violation%20of%20the%20Central%20Civil%20Services%20(Conduct)%20Rules%2C%201964%2C%20which%20directs%20that%20no%20government%20servant%20shall%20take%20part%20in%20any%20political%20activity.%20While%20it%20is%20acceptable%20for%20government%20officers%20to%20disseminate%20information%2C%20to%20make%20them%20%E2%80%9Ccelebrate%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cshowcase%E2%80%9D%20achievements%20blatantly%20turns%20them%20into%20political%20workers%20of%20the%20ruling%20party%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kharge%20wrote%20in%20his%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20soldiers%20becoming%20%E2%80%9Cmarketing%20agents%20for%20government%20schemes%E2%80%9D%20would%20count%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdangerous%20step%20towards%20%5Bthe%5D%20politicisation%20of%20the%20armed%20forces%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EFor%20the%20Modi%20Govt%2C%20all%20agencies%2C%20institutions%2C%20arms%2C%20wings%2C%20and%20departments%20of%20the%20government%20are%20now%20officially%20%E2%80%98Pracharaks%E2%80%99%20!%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20view%20of%20protecting%20our%20democracy%20and%20our%20Constitution%2C%20it%20is%20imperative%20that%20the%20orders%20which%20would%20lead%20to%20the%20politicising%20of%20Bureaucracy%20and%20our%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Ft9hq0N4Ro4%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Ft9hq0N4Ro4%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20(%40kharge)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkharge%2Fstatus%2F1716005618224451906%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2022%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20seems%20like%20the%20Congress%20party%20is%20remembering%20a%20history%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20intent%20on%20forgetting.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20history%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20independent%20India%E2%80%99s%20political%20history%20is%20of%20any%20value%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20and%20his%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20by%20dint%20of%20that%20circular%2C%20have%20only%20thrown%20at%20today%E2%80%99s%20India%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20struggle%20of%20memory%20against%20forgetting%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20begin%20with%20the%20memory.%20On%20June%2012%2C%201975%2C%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20famously%20found%20the%20then%20prime%20minister%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20guilty%20of%20misusing%20official%20machinery%20in%20the%20Congress%20party%E2%80%99s%20election%20campaign%2C%20leading%20to%20her%20disqualification%20from%20contesting%20any%20election%20for%20six%20years%20in%20a%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20charge%20raised%20against%20her%20was%20that%20she%20had%20made%20use%20of%20the%20services%20of%20Yashpal%20Kapoor%2C%20the%20Congress%20gofer%20and%20her%20most%20important%20aide%20in%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Secretariat%2C%20to%20%E2%80%98further%20her%20election%20prospects%2C%2C%20thus%20breaking%20an%20electoral%20rule%20that%20forbade%20the%20use%20of%20state%20employees%20for%20private%20gain%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20Christophe%20Jaffrelot%20and%20Pratinav%20Anil%20in%20%3Cem%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20First%20Dictatorship%20%E2%80%93%20The%20Emergency%20(1975-77)%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20authors%20went%20on%20to%20also%20highlight%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20second%20trespass%3A%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20had%20also%20used%20state%20employees%2C%20this%20time%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20officials%2C%20to%20build%20the%20rostrums%20for%20her%20(election)%20rallies.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F31182212%2FIndira-Gandhi.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F31182212%2FIndira-Gandhi.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F31182212%2FIndira-Gandhi-300x198.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F31182212%2FIndira-Gandhi-1024x676.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-306534%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22792%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIndira%20Gandhi.%20Photo%3A%20Public.Resource.Org%2FFlickr%20CC%20BY%202.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%20judgment%20day%20also%20came%20as%20a%20double%20whammy%20for%20Indira%20Gandhi%20and%20her%20coterie%20because%20on%20that%20same%20June%20day%2C%20the%20Congress%20party%20took%20a%20drubbing%20in%20the%20crucial%20Gujarat%20elections.%20The%20Congress%20(I)%20lost%20140%20of%20the%20182%20seats%20in%20those%20polls%20to%20the%20Janata%20Morcha%2C%20and%20thereby%20lost%20power%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20that%20state.%20%E2%80%9CMrs%20Gandhi%20had%20run%20a%20strident%20campaign%2C%20staying%20in%20the%20state%20for%20eleven%20days%20and%20addressing%20119%20meetings.%20It%20was%20rare%20for%20a%20prime%20minister%20to%20take%20such%20keen%20interest%20in%20state%20politics%2C%20but%20the%20odd%20circumstances%20had%20demanded%20it%3A%20a%20massive%20wave%20of%20protest%20in%20Ahmedabad%20and%20other%20Gujarati%20cities%20had%20prompted%20the%20resignation%20of%20incumbents%20and%20the%20calling%20of%20fresh%20elections%2C%20offering%20the%20Congress%20the%20one%20chance%20it%20had%20to%20demonstrate%20its%20popular%20support%20and%20discredit%20the%20extra-parliamentary%20movement%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20Jaffrelot%20and%20Anil.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.narendramodi.in%2Femergency-gujarat-and-narendra-modi-3126%5C%22%3EBy%20his%20own%20admission%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Modi%2C%20then%20a%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20%3Cem%3Epracharak%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9Crisked%20his%20life%E2%80%9D%20to%20%E2%80%9Cwork%20wholeheartedly%20for%20restoring%20democracy%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%9D.%20His%20website%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6in%20fact%20Gujarat%20became%20role%20model%20for%20many%20who%20were%20against%20Emergency.%20It%20was%20the%20Navanirman%20movement%20of%20Gujarat%2C%20which%20made%20Congress%20realize%20that%20at%20least%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20their%20lust%20for%20power%20won%E2%80%99t%20last.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Political%20Strategy%20Lies%20in%20the%20Constant%20Use%20of%20Self-Image%20in%20the%20Religious%20Context%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-self-image-religion-politics-image%5C%22%3ENarendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Political%20Strategy%20Lies%20in%20the%20Constant%20Use%20of%20Self-Image%20in%20the%20Religious%20Context%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20recent%20circular%2C%20however%2C%20is%20an%20indication%20that%20his%20regime%20is%20doing%20more%20forgetting%20than%20remembering%20of%20those%20times.%20Take%20into%20account%20also%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20week-long%20jaunt%20to%20campaign%20in%20a%20state%20election%20difficult%20for%20his%20party%20%E2%80%93%20the%20recent%20Karnataka%20polls.%20Akin%20to%20Indira%20of%201975%2C%20Modi%20addressed%2019%20rallies%20and%20six%20road%20shows%2C%20but%20his%20party%20was%20still%20routed%2C%20as%20Indira%E2%80%99s%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20retired%20senior%20bureaucrat%2C%20who%20handled%20several%20elections%20and%20is%20now%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Constitutional%20Conduct%20Group%20but%20wants%20to%20remain%20anonymous%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20shocking%20that%20the%20Centre%20had%20issued%20such%20a%20circular%20at%20a%20time%20when%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20(MCC)%20is%20in%20place%20in%20four%20election-bound%20states%20where%20BJP%20is%20facing%20elections%20and%20the%202024%20parliamentary%20elections%20are%20just%20a%20few%20months%20away.%20It%20is%20a%20blatant%20violation%20of%20the%20Constitutional%20norm.%E2%80%9D%20He%20also%20underlined%2C%20%E2%80%9CLooking%20at%20the%20scale%20of%20misuse%20of%20power%20that%20comes%20across%20from%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20circular%2C%20what%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20did%20in%201971%20comes%20across%20as%20a%20minor%20offence%20and%20even%20then%20our%20judiciary%20rightly%20stood%20up%20against%20violation%20of%20the%20Constitution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20more%20a%20technical%20error%2C%20a%20%E2%80%98peccadillo%E2%80%99%20as%20the%20papers%20put%20it%2C%20for%20Kapoor%20had%20begun%20working%20on%20Mrs%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20on%20January%207%201971%20but%20had%20left%20his%20government%20position%20only%20six%20days%20later%2C%20remaining%20a%20state%20employee%20in%20the%20official%20records%20until%2025%20January%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jaffrelot%20and%20Anil%20had%20underlined%20in%20their%20book.%20The%20duo%20had%20also%20pointed%20out%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20stakes%20(of%20the%20judgment)%20were%20at%20once%20small%20and%20large%3A%20small%20because%20of%20the%20nature%20of%20offence%2C%20and%20large%20because%20of%20its%20implications.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20coming%20days%2C%20as%20the%20election%20fever%20only%20rises%2C%20political%20parties%20will%20likely%20rake%20this%20circular%20up%20against%20the%20Modi%20government%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20with%20some%20or%20the%20other%20even%20going%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20filing%20a%20petition%20or%20two%20in%20court.%20Here%2C%20it%20is%20worth%20jogging%20one%E2%80%99s%20memory%20that%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20order%20debarring%20Indira%20Gandhi%20from%20contesting%20elections%20had%20come%20after%20four%20years%20of%20hearings.%20Rumours%20were%20abound%20then%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20and%20enticement%20were%20bestowed%20by%20her%20party%20emissaries%20on%20Justice%20Jag%20Mohan%20Lal%20Sinha%20to%20deliver%20a%20favourable%20judgment.%20The%20judge%20stood%20by%20the%20Constitution%2C%20but%20it%20nevertheless%20brought%20on%20India%20the%20Emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESenior%20Supreme%20Court%20lawyer%20Sanjay%20Hedge%2C%20however%2C%20sees%20a%20fine%20line%20in%20the%20circular%20drawn%20between%20a%20party%20diktat%20on%20government%20officials%20and%20a%20government%E2%80%99s%20order%20to%20them%20to%20run%20an%20official%20programme.%20%E2%80%9CDespite%20the%20politically%20fraught%20nomenclature%2C%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%20the%20yatra%20is%20a%20government%20programme%20and%20government%20servants%20are%20being%20nominated%20for%20coordination.%20Legally%20it%20cannot%20be%20invalid.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHedge%20also%20thinks%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20analogy%20is%20misplaced%20here.%20%E2%80%9CHer%20election%20was%20set%20aside%20by%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20because%20an%20individual%20government%20servant%2C%20Yashpal%20Kapoor%2C%20had%20for%20a%20few%20days%20been%20her%20election%20agent%20despite%20being%20in%20government%20service.%20The%20Allahabad%20judgment%20was%20set%20aside%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20the%20Kapoor%20instance%2C%20as%20Jaffrelot%20and%20Anil%20had%20pointed%20out%2C%20the%20high%20court%20had%20also%20taken%20into%20account%20the%20use%20of%20UP%20government%20employees%20in%20election%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20poll%20season%2C%20the%20ball%20is%20certainly%20first%20in%20the%20Election%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20court%20to%20rise%20up%20to%20the%20challenge%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cstruggle%20of%20memory%20against%20forgetting%E2%80%9D.%20In%20its%20case%20this%20is%20of%20utmost%20significance%20%E2%80%93%20considering%20it%20would%20not%20only%20mean%20upholding%20the%20constitutional%20norms%20of%20%E2%80%98the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20democracy%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20among%20its%20primary%20duties%2C%20but%20also%20affirming%20its%20independence%20from%20the%20government%20of%20the%20day%2C%20a%20constitutional%20propriety%20it%20must%20adhere%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697977823000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F22171955%2FF8OlZAaXEAAeXHw.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmodi-government-move-to-turn-government-officers-into-rath-prabharis-stirs-storm%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Opposition%20parties%20are%20asking%20the%20Modi%20government%20tough%20questions.%20Former%20cabinet%20secretary%20B.K.%20Chaturvedi%20told%20The%20Wire%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20unprecedented.%20I%20have%20not%20seen%20any%20such%20thing%20in%20my%20entire%20civil%20service%20career.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A36%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmodi-government-move-to-turn-government-officers-into-rath-prabharis-stirs-storm%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Perfect%20storm%20sets%20up%20catastrophe%20bonds%20for%20record%20returns%20this%20year%20as%20investors%20price%20in%20climate%20costs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221996%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20fire%20whirl%20is%20seen%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20a%20wildfire%2C%20shooting%20a%20long%20strand%20of%20fire%20towards%20the%20sky.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65099cb4bf943d00195b7060%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22998%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20fire%20whirl%20shoots%20into%20the%20sky%20as%20flames%20from