oes%20occur%2C%20however%2C%20then%20the%20issuer%20uses%20investors'%20money%20to%20help%20pay%20out%20claims.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20have%20been%2024%20climate%20disaster%20events%20in%20the%20US%20this%20year%2C%20with%20losses%20exceeding%20%241%20billion%20each%2C%20many%20haven't%20been%20severe%20enough%20to%20trigger%20payouts.%20According%20to%20the%20Swiss%20Re%20Cat%20Bond%20Price%20Return%20Index%2C%20year-to-date%20total%20returns%20are%20clocking%20in%20at%2016.5%25%2C%20on%20track%20for%20a%20new%20high%20unless%20a%20catastrophe%20occurs%20in%20the%20next%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20cat%20bonds%20are%20largely%20insulated%20from%20other%20forces%20moving%20markets%20%E2%80%94%20like%20virus%20outbreaks%2C%20bank%20failures%2C%20or%20wars%20%E2%80%94%20and%20price%20fluctuations%20don't%20always%20mean%20yield%20fluctuations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20reason%20is%20that%20money%20invested%20in%20cat%20bonds%20goes%20into%20Treasurys.%20And%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fbonds%2Ftreasury-bond-crash-yields-auction-demand-market-supply-us-debt-2023-10%5C%22%3EUS%20yields%20have%20been%20going%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20returns%20on%20cat%20bonds%20have%20been%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECat%20bond%20yields%20have%20also%20been%20on%20the%20rise%20because%20investors%20demanded%20higher%20risk%20premiums%20to%20make%20up%20for%20the%20increased%20frequency%20of%20severe%20storms%20and%20wildfires%20over%20the%20past%20several%20years%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Moody's%20note%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20investors%20buy%20cat%20bonds%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInsurers%20and%20reinsurers%20often%20issue%20cat%20bonds%20to%20de-risk%20themselves.%20And%20with%20the%20climate%20threat%20growing%2C%20cat%20bond%20issuance%20this%20year%20reached%20%2410.3%20billion%20by%20the%20middle%20of%20August%2C%20above%20the%20%2410%20billion%20for%20all%20of%202022%2C%20according%20to%20Moody's.%20The%20market%20is%20on%20track%20to%20eclipse%20the%20record%20high%20of%20%2413.9%20billion%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20cat%20bonds'%20loss%20multiple%2C%20or%20the%20amount%20of%20money%20you%20could%20make%20versus%20the%20amount%20of%20money%20you%20could%20lose%2C%20has%20become%20more%20attractive%20for%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLoss%20multiples%20have%20more%20than%20doubled%20since%202021%2C%20which%20is%20a%20pretty%20big%20deal%2C%20actually%2C%26quot%3B%20Modu%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20investors%20are%20hedge%20funds%2C%20pension%20funds%20and%20other%20institutional%20investors.%20And%20they%20are%20looking%20for%20assets%20that%20won't%20swing%20in%20line%20with%20the%20broader%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInterest%20rate%20movements%20don't%20cause%20hurricanes%2C%26quot%3B%20Jeff%20Mohrenweiser%2C%20senior%20director%20at%20the%20Fitch%20rating%20agency%2C%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BSo%20they're%20somewhat%20independent%20and%20that's%20attractive%20to%20investors%20because%20now%20they%20can%20put%20some%20non-correlated%20or%20diversifying%20risk%20into%20their%20portfolio.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20cat%20bonds%20are%20typically%20considered%20junk%20bonds%2C%20he%20added%2C%20explaining%20that%20they're%20below%20investment%20grade%20because%20the%20probability%20of%20default%20is%20much%20higher%20compared%20to%20an%20investment-grade%20bond.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Modu%20thinks%20investors%20are%20getting%20concerned%20about%20the%20effect%20of%20climate%20change%20on%20returns%20in%20the%20broader%20insurance-linked%20securities%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20therefore%2C%20to%20avoid%20it%2C%20some%20investors%20are%20kind%20of%20flying%20to%20quality%20effectively%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20quality%20is%20cat%20bonds.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcatastrophe-bonds-climate-change-us-treasury-yields-disaster-insurance-costs-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697977801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652ef76cbe9edfa8eda33e8e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fbonds%2Fcatastrophe-bonds-climate-change-us-treasury-yields-disaster-insurance-costs-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Catastrophe%20bonds%20promise%20a%20high%20return%20if%20a%20certain%20natural%20catastrophe%20doesn't%20happen.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asoni%40insider.com%20(Aruni%20Soni)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A25%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fbonds%2Fcatastrophe-bonds-climate-change-us-treasury-yields-disaster-insurance-costs-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20Carries%20Out%20Rare%20Aerial%20Attack%20on%20Mosque%20in%20West%20Bank's%20Jenin%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20a%20rare%20move%2C%20the%20Israeli%20army%20has%20carried%20out%20an%20aerial%20attack%20on%20Jenin%20town%20in%20the%20northern%20West%20Bank%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67186178%5C%22%3Ereports%20the%20BBC%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20report%20quoting%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%20said%20two%20people%20have%20died%20in%20the%20attack%20made%20on%20the%20town%E2%80%99s%20Al-Ansar%20mosque.%20According%20to%20the%20health%20ministry%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%2C%20which%20runs%20a%20part%20of%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20since%20October%207%2C%20as%20many%20as%2089%20Palestinians%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20have%20died%20in%20Israeli%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20%3Cem%3EAl%20Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20said%20three%20people%20have%20also%20been%20injured%20in%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJustifying%20the%20aerial%20attack%20carried%20out%20on%20Sunday%2C%20the%20Israeli%20authorities%20said%20Hamas%20had%20been%20using%20the%20mosque%20compound%20since%20July.%20The%20BBC%20report%20said%20the%20Israeli%20Defence%20Forces%20(IDF)%20released%20images%20of%20what%20it%20said%20were%20entrances%20to%20the%20compound%2C%20alongside%20images%20of%20weapons%2C%20computers%20and%20security%20measures%20pictured%20at%20the%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20IDF%20did%20not%20confirm%20whether%20a%20plane%2C%20helicopter%20or%20drone%20had%20been%20used%20in%20the%20Jenin%20strike%20on%20Sunday%2C%20but%20Israeli%20media%20reported%20that%20it%20was%20a%20fighter%20jet.%20The%20reports%20said%20if%20confirmed%20it%20would%20be%20only%20the%20second%20time%20in%20about%20two%20decades%20that%20a%20fighter%20jet%20had%20hit%20a%20target%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20BBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Israeli%20military%20said%20the%20strike%20on%20the%20Al-Ansar%20mosque%20early%20on%20Sunday%20killed%20several%20members%20of%20Hamas%20and%20Palestinian%20Islamic%20Jihad%20who%20had%20been%20using%20the%20building%20as%20a%20command%20centre%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20%3Cem%3EAl%20Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697977463000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-carries-out-rare-aerial-attack-on-mosque-in-west-banks-jenin%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Israeli%20authorities%20said%20Hamas%20had%20been%20using%20the%20mosque%20compound%20since%20July.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-carries-out-rare-aerial-attack-on-mosque-in-west-banks-jenin%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kajol%2C%20Jaya's%20K3G-like%20reunion%20at%20Durga%20Puja%20pandal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A169797566300