Cencounters%E2%80%9D.%20During%20the%20same%20period%20%E2%80%93%20March%202017%20to%20September%202023%E2%80%94the%20police%20in%20UP%20also%20shot%20and%20injured%205%2C591%20persons%20in%20these%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20number%20of%20people%20shot%20by%20the%20police%20reflects%20the%20normalisation%20of%20the%20phenomenon.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReleasing%20the%20above%20figures%20at%20the%20Police%20Smriti%20Diwas%20(Police%20Commemoration%20Day)%20event%20in%20Lucknow%2C%20Adityanath%20said%20the%20%E2%80%9Chighest%20priority%E2%80%9D%20of%20his%20government%20was%20to%20strengthen%20law%20and%20order%20in%20the%20state%2C%20create%20a%20sense%20of%20security%20among%20the%20public%20and%20instil%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20fear%20of%20the%20law%20in%20criminals%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20government%20flaunts%20these%20%E2%80%9Cencounter%E2%80%9D%20killings%20and%20shootings%20as%20a%20hallmark%20of%20its%20%E2%80%9Czero%20tolerance%20policy%E2%80%9D%20against%20crime%2C%20human%20rights%20activists%20have%20regularly%20questioned%20these%20operations%20and%20called%20them%20staged%20killings%20rather%20than%20spontaneous%20shootouts.%20The%20police%20claim%20they%20shoot%20people%20only%20in%20retaliatory%20self-defence%2C%20a%20theory%20that%20is%20often%20under%20the%20scanner%20due%20to%20the%20similarities%20in%20the%20sequence%20of%20events%20and%20doubtful%20details%20of%20the%20alleged%20encounters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Lucknow%2C%20Adityanath%20also%20said%20that%20since%20March%202017%2C%2016%20police%20personnel%20had%20been%20killed%20while%201%2C478%20were%20injured%20in%20these%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20government%20has%20also%20in%20an%20unrestrained%20manner%20used%20the%20provisions%20of%20The%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Gangsters%20and%20Anti-Social%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%2C%201986%20against%20alleged%20criminals.%20The%20law%2C%20which%20allows%20the%20administration%20to%20designate%20people%20as%20gangsters%20and%20seize%20their%20property%2C%20has%20been%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20Adityanath%20government%E2%80%99s%20policing%20tactics%20even%20though%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20has%20on%20a%20few%20occasions%20expressed%20concerns%20that%20the%20state%20was%20misusing%20the%20Act.%20Opposition%20parties%20and%20activists%20have%20often%20accused%20the%20government%20of%20using%20the%20law%20to%20settle%20political%20scores%2C%20intimidate%20opponents%20and%20harass%20ordinary%20citizens.%20The%20BJP%20government%20has%20regularly%20invoked%20it%20against%20not%20just%20people%20designated%20as%20%E2%80%9Cmafia%E2%80%9D%20but%20also%20opposition%20party%20MLAs%20and%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20numbers%20speak%20for%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20Adityanath%20announced%20that%20ever%20since%20he%20came%20to%20power%2C%20the%20administration%20had%20slapped%20the%20Gangsters%20Act%20against%2069%2C332%20persons%20and%20the%20National%20Security%20Act%20against%20887%20persons.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20UP%20Gangsters%20Act%2C%20as%20it%20is%20better%20known%2C%20defines%20a%20gangster%20as%20a%20member%20or%20leader%20or%20organiser%20of%20a%20gang%20and%20includes%20any%20person%20who%20abets%20or%20assists%20in%20the%20activities%20of%20a%20gang.%20According%20to%20the%20Act%2C%20a%20gang%20is%20a%20group%20of%20persons%20who%20act%20either%20individually%20or%20collectively%20by%20violence%20or%20threat%20or%20show%20of%20violence%20or%20intimidation%20or%20coercion%20with%20the%20object%20of%20disturbing%20order%20or%20gaining%20any%20undue%20temporal%2C%20pecuniary%2C%20material%20or%20other%20advantage%20for%20himself%20or%20any%20other%20person.%20Section%2014%20of%20the%20contentious%20Act%20empowers%20the%20district%20magistrate%20to%20attach%20properties%20of%20alleged%20gangsters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdityanath%20said%20that%20his%20government%20had%20taken%20action%20against%2068%20such%20%E2%80%9Cmafia%E2%80%9D%20criminals%20and%20seized%2C%20demolished%20or%20freed%20property%20from%20illegal%20encroachment%20worth%20Rs%203%2C650%20crore.%20He%20claimed%20that%20at%20present%20there%20were%20no%20organised%20criminal%20gangs%20operating%20in%20the%20state%20outside%20jail.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20criminals%20have%20either%20been%20sent%20to%20jail%20or%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20police%20action%20during%20self-defence%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20police%20action%20had%20increased%20the%20sense%20of%20security%20among%20girls%2C%20women%2C%20weaker%20sections%20and%20traders.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESocial%20activist%20Rajeev%20Yadav%2C%20however%2C%20questions%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20tall%20claims%20on%20solving%20its%20law%20and%20order%20problem%20through%20the%20use%20of%20encounters.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20are%20saying%20that%20crime%20is%20being%20controlled%20through%20%E2%80%98encounters%E2%80%99%2C%20then%20why%20are%20they%20lodging%20an%20unprecedented%20number%20of%20cases%20under%20the%20Gangsters%20Act%20and%20Goonda%20Act%20and%20having%20to%20use%20bulldozers%20to%20demolish%20property%20even%20now%3F%E2%80%9D%20Yadav%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYadav%2C%20who%20has%20tracked%20the%20issue%20of%20extra-judicial%20killings%20in%20UP%2C%20says%20that%20while%20Adityanath%E2%80%99s%20claims%20on%20finishing%20off%20organised%20crime%20may%20be%20debatable%2C%20what%20is%20certain%20is%20that%20there%20is%20%E2%80%9Cmore%20state%20organised%20crime%20now%E2%80%9D.%20By%20this%20he%20means%20the%20normalisation%20of%20%E2%80%98encounter%E2%80%99%20shootings%20with%20impunity%20and%20for%20even%20the%20pettiest%20of%20crimes%20where%20the%20accused%20could%20be%20easily%20apprehended.%20For%20instance%2C%20Yadav%20said%2C%20in%20September%20police%20in%20Ambedkar%20Nagar%20shot%20two%20men%20on%20charges%20of%20causing%20the%20death%20of%20a%2016-year-old%20girl%20who%20was%20run%20over%20by%20a%20motorcycle%20after%20they%20pulled%20her%20dupatta.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20entrenched%20have%20%E2%80%98encounter%E2%80%99%20shootings%20and%20seizure%20of%20property%20become%20in%20day-to-day%20law%20and%20order%20tactics%20that%20every%20day%20the%20UP%20police%20DGP%20headquarters%20releases%20a%20bulletin%20listing%20these%20%E2%80%9Ccommendable%E2%80%9D%20actions.%20A%20rough%20calculation%20of%20the%20official%20figures%20shows%20that%20since%20March%202017%2C%20police%20have%20on%20average%20shot%20and%20injured%202.4%20persons%20daily%20and%20shot%20dead%202.4%20persons%20on%20average%20every%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2021%2C%20police%20in%20Hamirpur%20shot%20a%20rape%20accused%20and%20recovered%20a%20country-made%20weapon%20from%20him.%20The%20same%20day%2C%20police%20and%20administration%20in%20Kaushambi%20seized%20moveable%20and%20immovable%20property%20worth%20Rs%2019.30%20crore%20belonging%20to%20two%20associates%20of%20the%20late%20MP%20Atiq%20Ahmad%2C%20who%20was%20assassinated%20in%20full%20public%20view%20in%20police%20custody%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20in%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20breaches%20of%20security%20in%20recent%20years%20caught%20on%20camera.%20The%20action%20against%20Mohammad%20Saud%20and%20Mohammad%20Faiz%20was%20taken%20on%20the%20basis%20of%2016%20FIRs%20lodged%20against%20them%2C%20said%20police.%20These%20included%20cases%20of%20extortion%2C%20attempt%20to%20murder%2C%20murder%20and%20illegally%20occupying%20land.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20seized%20their%20residences%2C%20shops%2C%20plots%20and%20more%20than%2010%20vehicles%20under%20the%20Gangsters%20Act%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20Kaushambi%2C%20Brijesh%20Kumar%20Srivastava.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EActivist%20Rajeev%20Yadav%20says%20that%20while%20in%20Adityanath%E2%80%99s%20first%20tenure%2C%20%E2%80%98encounters%E2%80%99%20were%20used%20to%20send%20a%20political%20message%2C%20gradually%20with%20time%20they%20have%20become%20the%20preferred%20tactic%20of%20the%20police%20to%20show%20that%20it%20was%20tackling%20law%20and%20order%20problems.%20%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20the%20police%20want%20to%20maintain%20law%20and%20order%20through%20%E2%80%98encounters%E2%80%99%20and%20even%20the%20public%20in%20some%20cases%20are%20now%20equating%20them%20with%20justice.%20Police%20are%20carrying%20out%20%E2%80%98encounters%E2%80%99%20even%20in%20cases%20of%20ordinary%20crimes%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Yadav.%20He%20justifies%20his%20argument%20by%20referring%20to%20the%20recent%20killings%20of%20six%20persons%20over%20a%20land%20dispute%20in%20Deoria%20district%20where%20the%20lone%20survivor%20of%20one%20family%20had%20demanded%20that%20the%20police%20kill%20the%20accused%20from%20the%20other%20side%20in%20%E2%80%98encounters%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20scripts%20of%20the%20alleged%20encounters%20have%20an%20uncannily%20identical%20sequence%20of%20events%2C%20where%20police%20intercept%20the%20accused%20or%20accused%20persons%20or%20suspects%20in%20isolated%20locations%2C%20generally%20near%20a%20highway%2C%20a%20farm%20or%20a%20canal%2C%20or%20at%20checkpoints.%20The%20suspect%2C%20almost%20always%20riding%20a%20motorbike%2C%20finding%20himself%20surrounded%2C%20shoots%20at%20the%20police%20team%2C%20who%20fire%20back%20in%20self-defence%20and%20injure%20him%20with%20their%20bullet(s).%20In%20almost%20all%20cases%2C%20police%20recover%20a%20country-made%20pistol%20from%20the%20person%2C%20most%20commonly%20one%20that%20is%20315%20bore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20%E2%80%98encounter%E2%80%99%20shootings%20that%20took%20place%20in%20the%20state%20on%20October%2020%20follow%20this%20pattern.%20On%20the%20night%20of%20October%2019%2C%20police%20shot%20a%20person%20in%20Bulandshahr%20and%20recovered%20stolen%20jewellery%20from%20him.%20On%20October%2020%2C%20police%20shot%20two%20persons%20in%20Maharajganj%20and%20recovered%20Rs%2055%20lakh%20and%20gold%20(275%20grams)%20and%20silver%20(1.50kg)%20worth%20Rs%2012%20lakh%20from%20them.%20The%20items%20were%20stolen%20by%20the%20accused%20in%20a%20loot%20on%20October%2010%2C%20police%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Kushinagar%2C%20police%20force%20from%20five%20police%20stations%20along%20with%20the%20crime%20branch%20intercepted%20a%20wanted%20person%20near%20a%20canal%20and%20shot%20him%20after%20he%20allegedly%20fired%20at%20the%20police.%20In%20another%20incident%20in%20Bulandshahr%20on%20the%20same%20day%2C%20police%20intercepted%20a%20suspect%20near%20a%20flyover%20and%20shot%20him%20in%20an%20alleged%20exchange%20of%20fire.%20Police%20said%20they%20recovered%20a%20315%20bore%20pistol%2C%20a%20stolen%20motorcycle%20and%20Rs%208%2C700%20in%20cash%20that%20he%20had%20stolen.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fup-four-times-more-people-killed-in-police-action-under-adityanath-than-akhilesh-yadav%5C%22%3Ereported%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20August%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20four%20times%20more%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20%E2%80%98police%20action%E2%80%99%20during%20Adityanath%E2%80%99s%20first%20tenure%20from%202017%20to%202022%20in%20comparison%20with%20the%20government%20of%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20led%20by%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20(2012-2017).%20From%20the%20period%202017-18%20to%202021-2022%2C%20162%20persons%20were%20killed%20in%20%E2%80%9Cpolice%20action%E2%80%9D%20while%2041%20persons%20were%20killed%20from%202012%20to%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697970804000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F22160156%2FF88FtkFbAAAwMpn.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsince-adityanath-took-over-in-2017-up-police-have-killed-190-people-in-encounters%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20high%20number%20of%20people%20shot%20by%20the%20police%20reflects%20the%20normalisation%20of%20the%20phenomenon.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A25%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsince-adityanath-took-over-in-2