C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESaakhi%20is%20a%20Sunday%20column%20from%20Mrinal%20Pande%2C%20in%20which%20she%20writes%20about%20what%20she%20sees%20and%20also%20participates%20in.%20That%20has%20been%20her%20burden%20to%20bear%20ever%20since%20she%20embarked%20on%20a%20life%20as%20a%20journalist%2C%20writer%2C%20editor%2C%20author%2C%20and%20chairperson%20of%20Prasar%20Bharti.%20Her%20journey%20of%20being%20a%20witness-participant%20continues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20in%20primary%20school%2C%20we%20did%20not%20know%20or%20care%20about%20the%20Partition.%20Why%20would%20neighbours%20suddenly%20begin%20resenting%20each%20other%20enough%20to%20kill%20and%20set%20fire%20to%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20homes%3F%20Who%20gained%20or%20lost%20in%20wars%2C%20whether%20between%20nations%20or%20within%20one%20country%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETruth%20be%20told%2C%20sitting%20in%20a%20tiny%20school%20in%20a%20small%20town%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20we%20did%20not%20know%20where%20exactly%20Lahore%20was%2C%20or%20Sindh%20or%20Amritsar.%20Our%20parents%2C%20when%20they%20did%2C%20talked%20in%20hushed%20whispers%20about%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Partition%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Crefugees%E2%80%9D%20who%20had%20come%20streaming%20in%20and%20changed%20the%20profile%20of%20%E2%80%9Cour%E2%80%9D%20towns.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20little%20later%20in%20Nainital%2C%20we%20saw%20the%20terrible%2C%20unbelievable%20traumas%20some%20of%20our%20neighbours%2C%20who%20were%20landlords%20in%20Punjab%20before%20being%20driven%20out%20with%20next%20to%20nothing%20and%20turned%20into%20unwelcome%20refugees.%20One%20large%20family%20lived%20in%20a%20huge%20%3Cem%3Ekothi%3C%2Fem%3E%20next%20to%20ours.%20They%20were%20luckier%20than%20many%2C%20and%20had%20done%20very%20well%20with%20the%20land%20the%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20government%20had%20granted%20them%20in%20the%20terai%20region%20as%20compensation.%20However%2C%20memories%20of%20the%20Partition%20and%20a%20sudden%20loss%20of%20centuries%20old%20ro