indi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fbollywood-trivia-did-you-know-that-katrina-kaifs-introduction-scene-in-zindagi-na-milegi-dobara-was-shot-at-a-clothing-optional-beach-in-spain%2Farticleshow%2F104583968.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gaza%20Braces%20For%20More%20Fire%20As%20Israel%20Removes%20Risks%20Before%20Ground%20Offensive%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3EA%20key%20objective%20of%20Israel's%20ground%20offensive%20is%20to%20free%20the%20200-odd%20hostages%20taken%20by%20Hamas%20during%20the%20October%207%20attacks.%20Israel's%20military%20spokesperson%20Daniel%20Hagari%20has%20said%20the%20bombardment%20in%20Gaza%20will%20be%20intensified%20to%20minimise%20risks%20to%20troops%20when%20they%20enter%20the%20Strip%2C%20news%20agency%20AFP%20reported.%20The%20officer%20called%20upon%20Gaza%20city%20residents%20to%20move%20south%20for%20their%20safety.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EPalestinians%20have%20received%20renewed%20warnings%20from%20Israel's%20forces%20to%20move%20to%20the%20south%20of%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20news%20agency%20Reuters%20has%20reported.%20The%20fresh%20warning%20adds%20that%20they%20could%20be%20identified%20as%20sympathisers%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bterrorist%20organisation%26quot%3B%20if%20they%20stayed%20put.%20The%20message%20was%20delivered%20in%20leaflets%20marked%20with%20the%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20name%20and%20logo%20from%20Saturday%20and%20also%20sent%20to%20people%20via%20mobile%20phone%20audio%20messages.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EHamas%20on%20Friday%20released%20two%20hostages%20--%20US%20citizens%20Judith%20Tai%20Raanan%20and%20her%20daughter%20Natalie%20Shoshana%20Raanan.%20The%20mother-daughter%20pair%20was%20kidnapped%20from%20Nahal%20Oz%20kibbutz%20near%20the%20Israel-Gaza%20border%20on%20October%207.%20They%20were%20reportedly%20visiting%20Israel%20on%20a%20holiday.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EHamas%20has%20now%20claimed%20that%20they%20had%20offered%20to%20release%20two%20more%20hostages%20on