%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fjeff-bezos-old-amazon-review-of-milk-goes-viral-elon-musk-reacts-4504114%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fjeff-bezos-old-amazon-review-of-milk-goes-viral-elon-musk-reacts-4504114%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20We%20Know%20So%20Far%20About%20Congress%2C%20BJP%20Candidates%20in%20Rajasthan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F22112200%2FF84a12kXkAAI7Ua.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJaipur%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20After%20a%20long%20wait%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20released%20a%20list%20of%2033%20candidates%20who%20will%20contesting%20the%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Rajasthan.%20The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20unveiled%20its%20second%20list%20of%20candidates%2C%20which%20includes%2083%20names.%20The%20BJP%20had%20released%20its%20first%20list%20of%2041%20candidates%20on%20October%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20list%20has%20clarified%20that%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20and%20Sachin%20Pilot%20will%20be%20contesting%20from%20Sardarpura%20and%20Tonk%2C%20respectively.%20Earlier%2C%20there%20was%20speculation%20that%20both%20might%20change%20their%20constituencies%20and%20contest%20from%20different%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20also%20given%20tickets%20to%20three%20candidates%20who%20lost%20in%20the%202018%20elections%3A%20Archana%20Sharma%20from%20Malviya%20Nagar%2C%20Pushpendra%20Bharadwar%20from%20Sanganer%2C%20and%20Vivek%20Dhakad%20from%20Mandalgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EArchana%20Sharma%20lost%20the%20Malviya%20Nagar%20seat%20by%20a%20margin%20of%201%2C704%20votes%20to%20Kalicharan%20Saraf%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20who%20received%2070%2C221%20votes.%20The%20BJP%20has%20again%20fielded%20the%20same%20candidate%20in%20the%20Malviya%20Nagar%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDhakad%20lost%20to%20Gopal%20Lal%20Sharma%20from%20Mandalgarh%20by%20a%20margin%20of%2010%2C333%20votes.%20In%20its%20second%20list%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20cleared%20Gopal%20Lal%20Sharma%E2%80%99s%20name%20for%20the%20Mandalgarh%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPushpendra%20Bharadwar%20from%20Sanganer%20lost%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Ashok%20Lahoty%20by%20a%20margin%20of%2072%2C542%20votes.%20This%20time%2C%20Bhajan%20Lal%20Sharma%20will%20contest%20from%20Sanganer%20on%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20finalised%20144%20names%20out%20of%20the%20total%20200%20constituencies%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20with%2056%20names%20yet%20to%20be%20announced.%20Recently%2C%20Rajendra%20Rathore%2C%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frajendra-rathore-rajasthan-bjp-vasundhara-raje%5C%22%3Etold%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20an%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20complete%20list%20of%20candidates%20will%20be%20released%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20week%2C%20and%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20workers%20will%20be%20active%20on%20the%20ground.%20Rathore%20has%20also%20changed%20his%20constituency%20from%20Churu%2C%20where%20he%20won%20by%20a%20small%20margin%20of%201%2C850%20votes%20against%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Rafique%20Mandelia%2C%20to%20Taranagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20worth%20noting%20that%20the%20Congress%20has%20given%20a%20ticket%20to%20sitting%20MLA%20Danish%20Abrar%20from%20Sawai%20Madhopur%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%20has%20not%20announced%20a%20candidate%20for%20the%20same%20constituency.%20In%202018%2C%20only%20one%20Muslim%20candidate%2C%20Yoonus%20Khan%2C%20received%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20ticket%20in%20Rajasthan%20from%20the%20Tonk%20constituency%2C%20for%20which%20the%20BJP%20is%20yet%20to%20announce%20a%20candidate.%20Khan%20was%20the%20transport%20minister%20in%20Vasundhara%20Raje%E2%80%99s%20government%2C%20and%20sources%20suggest%20that%20he%20will%20contest%20the%20election%20if%20the%20party%20considers%20his%20name.%20Khan%20had%20lost%20to%20Pilot%20by%20a%20margin%20of%2054%2C179%20votes%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20speculation%20that%20Raje%20might%20contest%20from%20the%20Sardarpura%20constituency%2C%20which%20is%20the%20stronghold%20of%20the%20current%20chief%20minister%2C%20Ashok%20Gehlot.%20However%2C%20the%20list%20has%20clarified%20that%20Raje%20will%20be%20contesting%20from%20the%20Jhalrapatan%20seat%2C%20where%20she%20has%20a%20stronghold.%20Raje%20has%20been%20winning%20the%20Jhalrapatan%20seat%20since%202003.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENarpat%20Singh%20Rajvi%2C%20who%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20one%20of%20Raje%E2%80%99s%20loyalists%2C%20is%20nominated%20in%20the%20second%20list%20from%20Chittorgarh.%20Earlier%20in%20the%20first%20list%2C%20Rajvi%E2%80%99s%20name%20was%20dropped%20from%20his%20Vidhayadhar%20Nagar%20seat%2C%20which%20has%20now%20been%20given%20to%20Rajsamand%20MP%20Diya%20Kumari.%20Rajvi%20is%20the%20son-in-law%20of%20former%20chief%20minister%20Bhairon%20Singh%20Shekhawat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20leadership%20of%20the%20BJP%20appears%20chastised%20by%20protests%20breaking%20out%20over%20exclusion%20of%20several%20old-timers%2C%20especially%20Raje%20supporters%2C%20in%20the%20previous%20list.%20Many%20had%20confirmed%20they%20would%20be%20contesting%20as%20independents.%20Daily%20protests%20marked%20the%20announcement%20of%20tickets.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frajasthan-bjp-rebellion-first-list-publicly-opposed%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehad%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20troubles%20in%20the%20BJP%20earlier%2C%20and%20how%20Modi-Shah%20had%20been%20unable%20to%20control%20the%20rebellion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20second%20list%20has%20seen%20no%20MPs%20or%20prominent%20central%20leaders%20of%20the%20BJP%20being%20parachuted%20in.%20That%20is%20a%20departure%20from%20trends%20in%20Rajasthan%20earlier%20and%20also%20those%20seen%20in%20neighbouring%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20important%20seats%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20what%20used%20to%20be%20Gulabchand%20Kataria%E2%80%99s%20seat%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20given%20a%20ticket%20to%20Tarachand%20Jain%20from%20the%20Udaipur%20constituency.%20Jain%20is%20close%20to%20Assam%20governor%20Kataria.%20Jain%20is%20currently%20a%20councilor%20in%20the%20Udaipur%20Municipal%20Corporation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECongress%E2%80%99s%20Govind%20Singh%20Dotasara%20(the%20PCC%20chief%20in%20Rajasthan)%20will%20contest%20from%20Lachmangarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECongress%E2%80%99s%20Divya%20Maderna%2C%20who%20has%20criticised%20her%20own%20government%20several%20times%2C%20will%20be%20contesting%20from%20the%20Osian%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECongress%E2%80%99s%20C.P.%20Joshi%20will%20contest%20from%20Nathdwara.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20Satish%20Poonia%20will%20contest%20from%20Amber.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Kota%2C%20only%20one%20seat%E2%80%99s%20candidate%20has%20been%20announced%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20with%20Sandeep%20Sharma%20contesting%20from%20Kota%20South.%20Kota%20North%20candidates%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20announced%20by%20both%20parties.%20Currently%2C%20minister%20Shanti%20Dhariwal%20is%20the%20incumbent%20from%20Kota%20North.%20There%20is%20speculation%20that%20Shanti%20Dhariwal%20and%20Prahlad%20Gunjal%2C%20a%20former%20MLA%2C%20may%20not%20receive%20tickets%20for%20Kota%20North.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20are%20also%20yet%20to%20announce%20candidates%20for%20the%20Ladpura%20seat%20in%20Kota.%20This%20seat%20has%20been%20with%20the%20BJP%20since%202003%2C%20and%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Bhawani%20Singh%20Rajawat%20has%20been%20demanding%20the%20ticket.%20Rajawat%20was%20the%20MLA%20from%20Ladpura%20seat%20from%202003%20till%202018%20when%20he%20was%20denied%20ticket%20in%202018%20by%20the%20BJP.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20Ijyaraj%20Singh%20who%20was%20the%20